item.title: Data records of ‘Place of worship’, a religion map in GTA
item.description: Abstract This is a research project of local church/tempo etc in GTA, last updated 2006. People of different religions can have a clear idea of how where in GTA it has the places for them to worship. Also we can see the population divided by religion; and where exactly the places are, precisely, which neighborhood. Introduction This is a study of recording and organizing religious worship places in GTA, it is important for culture references not only for citizens, and also for the city government.
